import React from "react";

import "./ShowSVG.css"

const ShowSVG = () => {
    return (
        <svg className="showSVG" viewBox="0 0 48 48" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="#000000">
            <g id="SVGRepo_bgCarrier" strokeWidth="0"></g>
            <g id="SVGRepo_tracerCarrier" strokeLinecap="round" strokeLinejoin="round"></g>
            <g id="SVGRepo_iconCarrier"> 
                <path d="M0 0h48v48H0z" fill="none">
                </path> 
                <g id="Shopicon"> 
                    <circle cx="24" cy="24" r="4">
                    </circle> 
                    <path d="M24,38c12,0,20-14,20-14s-8-14-20-14S4,24,4,24S12,38,24,38z M24,16c4.418,0,8,3.582,8,8s-3.582,8-8,8s-8-3.582-8-8 S19.582,16,24,16z">
                    </path> 
                </g> 
            </g>
        </svg>
    )
}

export default ShowSVG;
